</b>110.19<b> Continue its efforts to adopt good governance and strengthen the role 
of the National Commission for Human Rights (Yemen); 
</b>110.20<b> Ensure compliance of the National Commission of Human Rights and 
Freedoms with the Paris Principles (France); 
</b>110.21<b> Implement successfully the national human rights policy and continue 
the process of incorporation of international human rights instruments into the 
national legislation (Azerbaijan); </b></p>


